    "description_long": "This stereo sound system consists of two rectangular black speaker units with a modern, minimalist design. The front face of each speaker features a large circular woofer and a smaller tweeter above it, both set in a dark wood-textured ring, with a horizontal bass port below. The sides and top are smooth and matte black, while the rear panels display dual terminal plates for speaker wire connections, each with red and black binding posts. The base of each speaker appears to have a subtle wooden accent, adding a touch of warmth to the otherwise sleek appearance. No visible control panels, screens, or branding are present on the exterior surfaces.",
